{"title":"黄山松","authors":["喻晓"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":7,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喻晓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"异乎寻常！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一丝隙缝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就能扎下根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萌发一个绿的梦想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无法想象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若没有松树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山会是一番什么风光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头是死的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云雾失去生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十六峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是三十六块墓碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山不过是大自然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一部苍凉的乐章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了枝干苍劲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"形态优美的古松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山才有了灵秀之气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画家才有了神来之笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人才有了动人心魄的千古绝唱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里没有青云直上的幸运儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是靠自身的努力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裂岩破石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一寸寸地生长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越是在艰难中生长的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越是美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越是不朽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句珍贵的箴言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写在千仞青壁之上！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}